{"word":"ὤλξ","slug":"ὤλξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὤλξ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:syncopated'>syncop.</a> for <el>ὦλαξ, αὖλαξ</el>\n<p/><i>a furrow</i>, only in <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <el>ὦλκα, ὦλκας</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Moschus'>Mosch.</a></b><p/>"}]}